title: (Fri Full) Tim McGraw Confessed the First Thing He Did After Filming Wrapped on ‘1883’ + Why Not To Let Your Dogs Lick You…
itunes:title: (Fri Full) Tim McGraw Confessed the First Thing He Did After Filming Wrapped on ‘1883’ + Why Not To Let Your Dogs Lick You…
description:
Tim McGraw stops by the studio to talk about his new tour, filming 1883 and the songs he recorded that he didn’t expect to be a hit. Bobby reveals in the news why you shouldn’t let your dog lick you. We also play a round of Easy Trivia as part of our Friday tradition.
